Bhidu, coding karna hai na? Chalo, ek simple C program likhte hain. Yeh program ek message print karega, "Hello, Bhidu!"

```c
#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    printf("Hello, Bhidu!\n");
    return 0;
}
```

Beta sun, ye program compile karne ke baad run kar, aur dekh, "Hello, Bhidu!" print hoga. Bhidu, ab tum try karo!
